INSERT INTO mod_history (
			mod_id, 
			author_id,
			date, 
			downloads_total,
			views,
			followers,
			favorited,
			votes_up,
			votes_down,
			score,
			num_comments,
			playtime,
			time_updated,
			version
		)
		SELECT * FROM UNNEST(
			$1::bigint[], 
			$2::bigint[],
			$3::date[], 
			$4::int[], 
			$5::bigint[], 
			$6::int[],
			$7::int[],
			$8::int[],
			$9::int[],
			$10::float8[],
			$11::int[],
			$12::bigint[],
			$13::bigint[],
			$14::text[]
		)
